		{"id":"900e5591583c3b25","type":"text","text":"$\\theta\\in[-\\pi,\\pi]$","x":247,"y":393,"width":116,"height":50,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"4a70335e1879f2ef","type":"text","text":"$R_{n,o}(\\omega)=\\mathcal{F}(\\omega)\\times G_{n,o}(\\omega, \\theta)$\n$O_{n,o}(x,y)=\\mathcal{F^{-1}}\\{R_{n,o}(w)\\}=e_{n,o}(x,y)+j.o_{n,o}(x,y)$","x":-246,"y":1016,"width":400,"height":89,"color":"1"},
